verbose_text: Activation of AdipoR1 and/or AdipoR2 by adiponectin stimulates the activation of peroxisome-proliferator-activated receptor-alpha (PPARalpha), AMP activated protein kinase (AMPK), and p38 mitogen activated protein kinase.
